OL,3,CBlack people in UK 'almost four times
OL,4,Cmore likely to become homeless'
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Producer, Jamel Smith
OL,8,FBlack people in the UK are almost four
OL,9,Ftimes more likely to face homelessness
OL,10,Fthan white people, and many say they
OL,11,Ffeel pressured to change their names,
OL,12,Faccents or hairstyles to avoid
OL,13,Fdiscrimination, new research shows.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
