OL,6,F"She said, somebody at work said,
OL,7,F'You're not a typical Black woman,'
OL,8,Fand she didn't react, but she said
OL,9,Fthat she understood immediately...My
OL,10,Fson has an all ethnic name and she was
OL,11,Ftelling me recently, you better change
OL,12,Fit."
OL,14,FSomeone else said: "I have a mixture
OL,15,Fof friends, but my white friends, they
OL,16,Fgot help immediately from the council.
OL,17,FI do feel like race plays a big part
OL,18,Fin it. I don't know."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
