OL,3,CBlack people in UK 'almost four times
OL,4,Cmore likely to become homeless'
OL,6,FHeriot-Watt University said the
OL,7,Ffindings expose a housing system that
OL,8,Fnot only fails to address existing
OL,9,Finequalities but actively reinforces
OL,10,Fthem through poor outcomes and
OL,11,Fdiscriminatory treatment.
OL,13,FProfessor Suzanne Fitzpatrick,
OL,14,Fdirector of I-SPHERE at Heriot-Watt
OL,15,FUniversity and the report's lead
OL,16,Fauthor, said: "The evidence is stark:
OL,17,FBlack people are almost four times
OL,18,Fmore likely to become homeless, and
OL,19,Fwhen they do access the statutory
OL,20,Fsystem, they face dramatically worse
OL,21,Foutcomes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
