OL,3,CBlack people in UK 'almost four times
OL,4,Cmore likely to become homeless'
OL,6,F"We have quantitative evidence that
OL,7,Ftheir outcomes are worryingly poor,
OL,8,Fand both qualitative and quantitative
OL,9,Fevidence that they face racial
OL,10,Fdiscrimination.
OL,12,F"This is a system that's supposed to
OL,13,Fhelp people in crisis, yet we're
OL,14,Fhearing accounts of callous, uncaring
OL,15,Fand unresponsive services."
OL,17,FShe said the study also reveals
OL,18,F"ethnic disparities in the risks,
OL,19,Fexperiences and outcomes associated
OL,20,Fwith homelessness in contemporary
OL,21,FEngland".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
