OL,3,CBlack people in UK 'almost four times
OL,4,Cmore likely to become homeless'
OL,6,F"This demands an urgent and wide-
OL,7,Franging response," she said. "We're
OL,8,Fnot just talking about poor housing
OL,9,Foutcomes here, we're talking in some
OL,10,Fcases about people feeling forced to
OL,11,Fdeny their own identity to access
OL,12,Fbasic services."
OL,14,FThe study also found that black
OL,15,Ffamilies are six times more likely to
OL,16,Flive in overcrowded homes than white
OL,17,Fhouseholds, while Pakistani and
OL,18,FBangladeshi households face the
OL,19,Fhighest rates of overcrowding, more
OL,20,Fthan seven times the white average.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
