OL,3,CBlack people in UK 'almost four times
OL,4,Cmore likely to become homeless'
OL,6,FMatt Downie, chief executive of the
OL,7,Fhomeless charity Crisis, said:
OL,8,F"Through their upcoming homelessness
OL,9,Fstrategy, the UK Government must take
OL,10,Fthe chance to root out racial
OL,11,Fdiscrimination and prejudice in our
OL,12,Fhousing and homelessness systems by
OL,13,Fadopting the recommendations in this
OL,14,Freport.
OL,16,F"For social housing, we would like to
OL,17,Fsee the Government go further by
OL,18,Fensuring providers allocate homes to
OL,19,Fpeople experiencing homelessness from
OL,20,Fall backgrounds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
