OL,6,F"Removing these structural barriers
OL,7,Fwould allow people to rebuild their
OL,8,Flives and leave homelessness behind
OL,9,Ffor good, regardless of their
OL,10,Fbackground, race or identity."
OL,12,FThe report urges the government to use
OL,13,Fits upcoming cross-departmental
OL,14,Fhomelessness strategy to tackle the
OL,15,Fdisproportionate impact on minoritised
OL,16,Fcommunities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
