OL,6,FIt calls for greater accountability at
OL,7,Fall levels, action on racism among
OL,8,Fprivate landlords, and a complete
OL,9,Foverhaul of how the asylum and
OL,10,Fhomelessness systems are connected.
OL,12,FA Ministry of Housing, Communities and
OL,13,FLocal Government spokesperson
OL,14,Freiterated to ITV News that racism in
OL,15,FBritain's housing system is illegal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
