OL,6,FThey said: "Racism in our housing
OL,7,Fsystem is illegal, and we urge anyone
OL,8,Fwho has suffered from discrimination
OL,9,Fto report it so it can be investigated
OL,10,Fand we can put an end to this
OL,11,Fdisgraceful behaviour.
OL,13,F"We are also taking urgent action to
OL,14,Ffix the housing crisis we inherited so
OL,15,Fpeople do not need to access these
OL,16,Fservices in the first place, including
OL,17,Fproviding #1 billion for crucial
OL,18,Fhomelessness services this year."
